{
  "text": "While such research describes the rich use cases for the application of AI for academic writing, they do not solicit indepth student perspectives to gain the necessary insight to optimize the use of this technology by learners and are mostly limited to close-ended survey items such as \"I've used AI-generated essay outlines to efficiently arrange my ideas before writing\" (Malik et al., 2023).",
